IMF GDP data

Source: R/data.R
imf.Rd

GDP at constant price for 2020&2021 from IMF

imf

Format

A data frame with 193 rows and 8 variables:

ISO

character iso3 country code

Country

character Country name

Units

character Units of the data

Scale

logical

Country/Series-specific Notes

character Data source

2020

double GDP data for 2020

2021

character GDP data for 2021

Estimates Start After

double Estimate time

Source

https://www.imf.org
